name: new XXL format sumynonazine editie 13.0 & 14.0 2022 leaf-thru
description:
this is an accessory NFT to show the new DOUBLE-WIDE format! yes bigger is, in fact, better. needless to say our costs for shipping and printing have gone up. these artists need to get some flow (aka tezos) out of this sometimes monthly, sometimes when we can get it out at all, next-level anon print and digital collaboration.

the zine is basically an all-inclusive, no-gatekeeping, thinly-veiled fundraising mechanism for artists. it mainly works when people buy our NFTs. we want the zine to be free to read! the whole thing! all the time! as we do, the artists so far donated their time and efforts, so we can only do them right after-the-fact. let's do them right! #web3
